      <details>
        <summary>How do I calculate my hours for a time sheet?</summary>
        <p>To calculate your hours, take your end time and subtract your start time. Convert the result to a decimal (e.g., 30 minutes becomes 0.5 hours), then subtract any unpaid breaks.</p>
      </details>
